Jason J. Lewis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jason_J._Lewis 0 Jason J. Lewis (born June 28, 1976 in Torrance, California) is an American actor and voice actor, best known for voicing Superman and other DC Comics characters on the Cartoon Network show Justice League Action.
